{"tid":2220672,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"十二隻恐龍去野餐","createTime":"2020-09-27T23:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T10:15:44.000Z","uid":99883,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd9c17b154fd7aee69b3769ab0bd08e73bdf5ee","tid":2220672,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T23:07:34.000Z","msg":"十二個港人被送中<br />\n<span class=\"red\">齊乘坐旅遊車出發了<br />\n路上唱歌謠快快樂樂<br />\nSing I am on my way<br />\n<br />\n又越過冰河 噴火山都穿過<br />\n二十里車程轉眼到<br />\n十二塊笑臉在齊去呼叫<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\n<br />\n白石嶺公園 到處青蔥一片<br />\n讓活潑恐龍通處跳<br />\n十二塊笑臉在齊野餐了<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\n六十罐曲奇吃個飽<br />\n愛吃的粟米乾乾脆脆<br />\n讓愉快心情快快樂樂<br />\nI am so happy<br />\n<br />\n莫亂棄果皮 你我記緊清潔<br />\n莫令這公園污染了<br />\n十二塊笑臉在齊說知道<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\n<br />\n白石嶺公園 這裡風景真美<br />\n讓活潑恐龍嬉戲<br />\n十二塊笑臉在齊野餐了<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\nMerrilly Merrilly<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"38bc6b8d135828ce33c7a38c344cf0a47284b5c4","tid":2220672,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T23:29:01.000Z","msg":"齊乘坐洗頭艇出發了"},{"pid":"2cc7cbd63dd6f65d935d35b936d1a68e443494ef","tid":2220672,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T23:30:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f473576b9a05ca634fcc3435ee777b1ecf4ccd9b","tid":2220672,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccf42458b33c7206d8bb8a3186eba2b33a43d4b","tid":2220672,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"改到引起關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}